{"id":9242,"date":"2024-03-30T17:23:42","date_gmt":"2024-03-30T17:23:42","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:10011\/?p=9242"},"modified":"2024-03-30T17:23:42","modified_gmt":"2024-03-30T17:23:42","slug":"sbs-application-form-2024","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sbs-application-form-2024\/","title":{"rendered":"SBS Application Form 2024 | Southern Business School"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong>SBS Application Form 2024, Southern Business School Application 2024, SBS Online Application 2024 Opening Date, SBS Online Application 2024 Closing Date, Up Online Application<\/strong><\/span><\/p><div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_64 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-light-blue ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >Contents on This Page<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sbs-application-form-2024\/#What_to_Know_About_the_Southern_Business_School_Application_Form_Portal\" title=\"What to Know About the Southern Business School Application Form Portal\">What to Know About the Southern Business School Application Form Portal<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sbs-application-form-2024\/#Who_is_Eligible_to_Apply_for_Admission\" title=\"Who is Eligible to Apply for Admission\">Who is Eligible to Apply for Admission<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sbs-application-form-2024\/#How_to_Apply_SBS_Application_Form_2024\" title=\"How to Apply | SBS Application Form 2024\">How to Apply | SBS Application Form 2024<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sbs-application-form-2024\/#Southern_Business_School_Application_Required_Documents\" title=\"Southern Business School Application Required Documents\">Southern Business School Application Required Documents<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sbs-application-form-2024\/#Closing_Date\" title=\"Closing Date\">Closing Date<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>\u00a0<\/strong>To apply for admission into the Southern Business School SBS Application Form 2024, kindly follow the <a href=\"https:\/\/stadio.ac.za\/southern-business-school-now-stadio-higher-education\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">link<\/a> and apply online. All applications must be submitted online<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"what-to-know-about-the-southern-business-school-application-form-portal\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_to_Know_About_the_Southern_Business_School_Application_Form_Portal\"><\/span>What to Know About the Southern Business School Application Form Portal<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The Southern Business School SBS Application portal is designed to accept application of candidates seeking for admission into the University. In the portal, applicant can Purchase application form, Track and monitor application status<a href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\">,<\/a> pay fees, Print Acknowledgement Slip, check admission list, etc.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"who-is-eligible-to-apply-for-admission\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Who_is_Eligible_to_Apply_for_Admission\"><\/span>Who is Eligible to Apply for Admission<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To be eligible for admission in the SBS application portal, candidates must;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Have Secondary School Leaving Certificate<\/li>\n<li>Meet National Senior Certificate (NSC) requirement for admission into Higher Certificate<\/li>\n<li>Grade 12 certificate applicant is of added advantage<\/li>\n<li>Must write the NBTs for admission to SBS on\/before 15 October 2024.<\/li>\n<li>FPS of 480 or above.<\/li>\n<li>NBT scores of Upper<\/li>\n<li>Intermediate for AL &amp; QL<\/li>\n<li>Mathematics 60%<\/li>\n<li>English HL 50%<\/li>\n<li>English FAL 60%<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply-sbs-application-form-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Apply_SBS_Application_Form_2024\"><\/span>How to Apply | SBS Application Form 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Eligible candidates can <a href=\"https:\/\/stadio.ac.za\/southern-business-school-now-stadio-higher-education\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">click here to apply<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Follow the steps below<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit Application portal<\/li>\n<li>Choose type of Application (Undergraduate, Post Graduate, Semester Studies)<\/li>\n<li>Fill and complete all necessary pages<\/li>\n<li>Pay Application fees where required<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-9033\" src=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/apply.zp141926-300x180.webp\" alt=\"SBS Application Form 2024 | Southern Business School\" width=\"300\" height=\"180\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"southern-business-school-application-required-documents\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Southern_Business_School_Application_Required_Documents\"><\/span><strong>Southern Business School Application Required Documents<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To apply to SBS you need to submit the following documentation:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>A completed application form<\/li>\n<li>A copy of your results for the latest school year<\/li>\n<li>A copy of your ID<\/li>\n<li>If you have attended another higher education institution, we need a copy of your academic transcript<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"closing-date\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Closing_Date\"><\/span>Closing Date<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>July 31, 2024<\/p>\n<p>For more information regarding the application for admission into the Southern Business School, kindly drop your messages in the comment box below.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"SBS Application Form 2024, Southern Business School Application 2024, SBS Online Application 2024 Opening Date, SBS Online Application&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9242"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.or